      "text": "Un wiꞥſch aizinaja Moh- fu un Aâronu Nakti/ un fazzija: Zelleetees/ eite ahra no mannu Lauschu Widdus/tik labbi juhs/ ka Israëta Behrni / un no-eite / kalpojeet tam KUNGAM pehz juhſeim Wahrdeem."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nemineet arridsan lihds juhsns fihkus un feelus Lohpusl/ ittin ka juhs effat runnajschi/ un no-eite / un fivehtijeet mann ar- ridſan."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Egipteri speede tohs Gândis ahtri no tahs Semmes isdsiht / jo tee fazzija : Mums wiſſeem jamirst."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Landis uszehle fa- wu Mihklu/ pirms ta farandseta bija/ un neffe tohs Mihklas Gab- valus ſawâs Drehbês eefetas us fawahm Plezzehm."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Israëta Behrni bij darrijschi pehz Mohsus Wahrda/ un praſſijscht no teem Egiptereem Sudraba-Rihkus / un Selta- Rihkus/ un Drehbes."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS bij arri teem Landim Schehlastibu dewis preekſch teem Egiptereem/ ka tee winneem aisdeive/ un winni ap- laupija tohs Egipterus."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta atsgahje Israëta Behr- ni no Raënſes lihds Sukotam / feſch ſimts tuhſtofschi Wihri bes Behrneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir ar teem wiſſadi Lau- dis/un fihti Lohpi/un leeli Lohpi/ warren dauds Lohpu."
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee zeppe no tah las/ ko tee no Egiptes- E bij neﬀuschi nerandsetas fchas/ jo ta ne bija fara jo tee tappe isdsihti no O Semmes/ un tee ne wa wetes / nedg arridsan Ze- ribu preekſch ſewim taifi"
    },
    {
      "n": 40,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu Israëta Mischanas Laiks / ko giptes Semmê mittuf- tschetrtints un trihs Gaddi."
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tee tschetr trihsdefinitgs Gaddi pag bija/ tad notifke tas/ itt schâ Deena/ tad isgahje KUNGA Spehks no Semmes."
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Scho Nakti bu KUNGAM fivehtu tur pehz ka wiꞥſch tohs no Semmes isweddis irr/ Nakts / kas tam KU N buhs turreta tapt no wi fraëta Behrneem."
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas KUNG ns Mohsu un Aâronu: tahs Passas Gestahdisch weenam Sweſchineekam ta ehſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr ikwee Naudu pirfkam Kalpa to/ kad wiꞥſch apgraisib no ta ehſt."
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne weenam Eeg nedg Algadschaim buhs"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weenâ Namme ehſt / junis no tahs G buhs ne neeka no ta Nan"
